<HEADLINE>
CARDINALS HEAVE BIG SIGH OF RELIEF 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By DAVID CASSTEVENS  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
