</P>
<P>
   ``The Wonderful World of Disney''
</P>
<P>
   ``World's Funniest ... ''
</P>
<P>
   ``The X-Files''
</P>
<P>
   EXISTING SHOWS MOVING FROM SUNDAY
</P>
<P>
   ``King of the Hill'' to Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
   ``The Jamie Foxx Show'' to Thursday.
</P>
<P>
   EXISTING SHOWS NEW TO SUNDAY
</P>
