   ``7th Heaven'' (reruns).
</P>
<P>
   ``Sister, Sister.''
</P>
<P>
   ``Smart Guy.''
</P>
<P>
   ``20/20'' (additional show).
</P>
<P>
   SUNDAY SHOWS GONE FOR GOOD
</P>
<P>
   (UNLESS OTHERWISE NOTED)
</P>
<P>
   ABC Sunday Night Movie
</P>
<P>
   ``Alright Already''
</P>
<P>
   ``Jenny''
</P>
<P>
   ``Men Behaving Badly''
</P>
<P>
   ``Nick Freno: Licensed Teacher''
</P>
<P>
   ``The Parent 'Hood'' (returning midseason)
</P>
<P>
   ``The Tom Show''
</P>
<P>
   ``You're the One''
</P>
</TEXT>
