<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-09-06 17:45 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1597 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-COMPUTER-YACHT-ART-86     09-06 0926
