u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KUROSAWA-FILMOGRAPHY-     09-06 0201
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-KUROSAWA-FILMOGRAPHY-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
50 YEARS OF AKIRA KUROSAWA FILMS 
</HEADLINE>
  (With OBIT-KUROSAWA) 
(jw) 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Akira Kurosawa had held a number of assistant and chief
assistant director jobs before finally releasing his first film at
the age of 33. Here is a list of his films and the year each was
released.:
</P>
