<TEXT>
<P>
   The Seattle Post-Intelligencer plans to move the following
stories for clients of the NYTimes News Service for editions of
Monday, Aug. 10, and thereafter. If you have any questions, please
call Lisa Schnellinger on the national-foreign desk at (206)
448-8035.
</P>
